014-10-06#Added#{2}":[2744,2745],"#Change Log#0.1.0 - 2014-10-06":[2746,2845],"#Change Log#0.1.0 - 2014-10-06#Added":[2748,2845],"#Change Log#0.1.0 - 2014-10-06#Added#{1}":[2750,2751],"#Change Log#0.1.0 - 2014-10-06#Added#{2}":[2752,2845]},"outlinks":[{"title":"includes a bunch of critical bug fixes","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/tz/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md#v102---2024-09-14","line":15},{"title":"#3885","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/3885","line":19},{"title":"#3886","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/3886","line":23},{"title":"Read more about the release in the announcement blog post","target":"https://blog.date-fns.org/v40-with-time-zone-support/","line":31},{"title":"Sasha @kossnocorp","target":"https://twitter.com/kossnocorp","line":33},{"title":"`@date-fns/tz`","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/tz","line":37},{"title":"README","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/tz","line":37},{"title":"open an issue","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/new","line":67},{"title":"report them","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/new","line":69},{"title":"@seated","target":"https://github.com/seated","line":77},{"title":"for sponsoring me","target":"https://github.com/sponsors/kossnocorp","line":77},{"title":"Fixed weeks in the Belarisuan locale's `formatDistance`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3720","line":81},{"title":"See the CDN guide.","target":"https://date-fns.org/docs/CDN","line":85},{"title":"Added CDN versions of modules compatible with older browsers.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3737","line":85},{"title":"@seated","target":"https://github.com/seated","line":89},{"title":"for sponsoring me","target":"https://github.com/sponsors/kossnocorp","line":89},{"title":"Fixed functions that use current date internally and made them work with date extensions like `UTCDate`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/3730","line":93},{"title":"Fixed `daysToWeeks` returning negative 0.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/commit/882ced61c692c7c4a79eaaec6eb07cb9c8c9195b","line":95},{"title":"Fixed German grammar for the \"half a minute\" string.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3715","line":97},{"title":"Added the Northern Sámi (`se`) locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3724","line":101},{"title":"@seated","target":"https://github.com/seated","line":107},{"title":"for sponsoring me","target":"https://github.com/sponsors/kossnocorp","line":107},{"title":"Added `roundToNearestHours` function.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2752","line":111},{"title":"Added Central Kurdish (`ckb`) locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3421","line":113},{"title":"Fixed the Czech locale's `formatDistance` to include `1` in `formatDistance`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3269","line":137},{"title":"#1391","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/1391","line":141},{"title":"Added a preprocessor to the locales API, enabling fixing a long-standing bug in the French locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3662","line":141},{"title":"Added `format` alias `formatDate` with corresponding `FormatDateOptions` interface","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3653","line":149},{"title":"#3641","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/3641","line":157},{"title":"Fixed inconsistent behavior of `roundToNearestMinutes`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3132","line":159},{"title":"Fixed the plural form of weeks in Swedish","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3448","line":171},{"title":"Added `yearsToDays` function","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3540","line":175},{"title":"See #2950","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/2950","line":177},{"title":"#3614","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/3614","line":185},{"title":"Fixed bug in `areIntervalsOverlapping` caused by incorrect sorting","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3628","line":185},{"title":"Fixed internal `toDate` not processing string arguments properly","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3626","line":193},{"title":"#3623","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/3623","line":201},{"title":"the Masquerading as CJS problem","target":"https://github.com/arethetypeswrong/arethetypeswrong.github.io/blob/main/docs/problems/FalseCJS.md","line":207},{"title":"yet another issue caused by ESM types","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/3620","line":213},{"title":"Added `package.json` to exports","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3601","line":215},{"title":"Fixed TypeScript 5.4 build break","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3598","line":217},{"title":"Fixed an error","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3618","line":223},{"title":"like Next.js","target":"https://twitter.com/kossnocorp/status/1731181274579325260","line":237},{"title":"please contact me","target":"mailto:koss@nocorp.me","line":263},{"title":"please contact me","target":"mailto:koss@nocorp.me","line":265},{"title":"UTCDate","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/utc","line":275},{"title":"See more details","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/3208#issuecomment-1528592465","line":289},{"title":"Fixed Ukrainian (`uk`) locale grammar for `formatDistance`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3175","line":297},{"title":"Improved browser compatibility by transforming the code with `@babel/preset-env`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3167","line":299},{"title":"Fixed `sv` locale abbreviated months matcher.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3160","line":307},{"title":"Fixed `uk` locale abbreviated months matcher.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3139","line":309},{"title":"Fixed a breaking change in `intervalToDuration` by removing a recently introduced RangeError.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3153","line":311},{"title":"Fixed TypeScript and flow types for daysInYear constant.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3125","line":319},{"title":"Added `intlFormatDistance` function`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2173","line":327},{"title":"Added `setDefaultOptions` and `getDefaultOptions` functions that allow you to set default default locale, `weekStartsOn` and `firstWeekContainsDate`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3069","line":329},{"title":"Added `roundingMethod` option to `roundToNearestMinutes`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3091","line":331},{"title":"Added Swiss Italian locale (`it-CH`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2886","line":333},{"title":"#2061","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/2061","line":335},{"title":"Added Occitan (`oc`) locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2106","line":335},{"title":"Added Belarusian Classic (`be-tarask`) locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3115","line":337},{"title":"Fixed Azerbaijani (`az`) locale for `formatDistance`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2924","line":341},{"title":"Fixed Czech (`cs`) locale for `parse`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3059","line":343},{"title":"Fixed TypeScript types for constants.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2941","line":345},{"title":"Fixed long formatters in the South African English locale (`en-ZA`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3014","line":347},{"title":"Fixed a typo in the Icelandic locale (`is`) for `format`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2974","line":349},{"title":"Fixed weekday format for `formatRelative` in the Portuguese locale (`pt`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2992","line":351},{"title":"Fixed `intervalToDuration` being off by 1 day sometimes.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2616","line":353},{"title":"Fixed ordinal number formatting in Italian locale (`it`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1617","line":355},{"title":"Fixed issue parsing months in Croatian (`hr`), Georgian (`ka`) and Serbian (`sr` and `sr-Latn`) locales.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2898","line":357},{"title":"Replaced `git.io` links with full URLs in error messages.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3021","line":361},{"title":"_Internal_: removed \"v2.0.0 breaking changes\" section from individual function docs","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2905","line":363},{"title":"Added West Frisian (`fy`) locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2183","line":371},{"title":"Added Uzbek Cyrillic locale (`uz-Cyrl`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2811","line":373},{"title":"add the missing accent mark for Saturday in Spanish locale (`es`) for `format`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2869","line":377},{"title":"allowed `K` token to be used with `a` or `b` in `parse`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2814","line":379},{"title":"Fixed translation for quarters in `format` in Chinese Simplified locale (`zh-CN`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2771","line":387},{"title":"Fixed `P` token in `format` for Romanian locale (`ro`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2213","line":389},{"title":"Fixed era and month formatters in Azerbaijani locale (`az`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1632","line":391},{"title":"Fixed `formatRelative` patterns in Georgian locale (`ka`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2797","line":393},{"title":"Fixed regular expressions for `parse` in Estonian locale (`er`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2038","line":395},{"title":"Fixed the format of zeros in `formatDuration` in Czech locale (`cs`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2579","line":397},{"title":"Fixed ordinal formatting for years, weeks, hours, minutes and seconds in `fr`, `fr-CA` and `fr-CH` locales.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2626","line":399},{"title":"Fixed constants not having proper TypeScript and Flow types.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2791","line":401},{"title":"Fixed translation for Monday in Turkish locale (`tr`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2720","line":403},{"title":"Fixed `eachMinuteOfInterval` not handling intervals less than a minute correctly.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2603","line":405},{"title":"Fixed flow types for `closestTo` and `closestIndexTo`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2781","line":407},{"title":"Added Khmer locale (`km`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2713","line":411},{"title":"Fixed `formatRelative` format for `lastWeek` in Spanish locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2753","line":419},{"title":"Fixed translation for October in Hindi locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2729","line":421},{"title":"Fixed Azerbaijani locale to use correct era matchers for `parse`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1633","line":423},{"title":"Added the functions that use `weekStartsOn` and `firstWeekContainsDate` that were missing from the `Locale` documentation page.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2652","line":425},{"title":"Changed abbreviation for August from \"Ags\" to \"Agt\" in Indonesian locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2658","line":429},{"title":"Added Irish English locale (`en-IE`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2772","line":433},{"title":"#1670","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/1670","line":435},{"title":"Added Arabic locale (`ar`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2721","line":435},{"title":"#2684","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/2684","line":437},{"title":"Added Hong Kong Traditional Chinese locale (zh-HK).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2686","line":437},{"title":"Added Egyptian Arabic locale (ar-EG).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2699","line":439},{"title":"Added Japanese Hiragana locale (`ja-Hira`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2663","line":447},{"title":"Added standalone months support to `de` and `de-AT` locales.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2602","line":449},{"title":"Adriaan Callaerts","target":"http://github.com/call-a3","line":453},{"title":"Koussay Haj Kacem","target":"http://github.com/essana3","line":453},{"title":"fturmel","target":"http://github.com/fturmel","line":453},{"title":"Jan Ziemba","target":"http://github.com/janziemba","line":453},{"title":"Jonas L","target":"http://github.com/jooola","line":453},{"title":"Kentaro Suzuki","target":"http://github.com/kentaro84207","line":453},{"title":"Sasha Koss","target":"http://github.com/kossnocorp","line":453},{"title":"Lucas Silva","target":"http://github.com/LucasHFS","line":453},{"title":"Deepak Gupta","target":"http://github.com/Mr-DG-Wick","line":453},{"title":"Anastasia Kobzar","target":"http://github.com/rikkalo","line":453},{"title":"Tan75","target":"http://github.com/tan75","line":453},{"title":"#2083","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/2083","line":457},{"title":"Fixed an edge case in the Slovak locale caused by unescaped character.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2540","line":457},{"title":"#2505","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/2505","line":461},{"title":"Used `1` instead of `ein` for German `formatDuration` to make it consistent with other locales and formats.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2576","line":461},{"title":"#2469","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/2469","line":463},{"title":"Made Norwegian `formatDuration` consistent with other locales by using numeric representation instead of written.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2631","line":463},{"title":"Use the word \"sekunda\" instead of \"vteřina\" for second in the Czech locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2577","line":465},{"title":"Made Flemish short date format corresponds to the Flemish government.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2535","line":467},{"title":"#2555","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/2555","line":471},{"title":"Added `roundingMethod` option to `differenceInHours`, `differenceInMinutes`, `differenceInQuarters`, `differenceInSeconds` and `differenceInWeeks` with `trunc` as the default method.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2571","line":471},{"title":"Added new functions: `previousDay`, `previousMonday`, `previousTuesday`, `previousWednesday`, `previousThursday`, `previousFriday`, `previousSaturday` and `previousSunday`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2522","line":473},{"title":"Branislav Lazic","target":"http://github.com/BranislavLazic","line":477},{"title":"fturmel","target":"http://github.com/fturmel","line":477},{"title":"Takuya Uehara","target":"http://github.com/indigolain","line":477},{"title":"Felipe Armoni","target":"http://github.com/komyg","line":477},{"title":"Sasha Koss","target":"http://github.com/kossnocorp","line":477},{"title":"Liam Tait","target":"http://github.com/Liam-Tait","line":477},{"title":"Maxim Topciu","target":"http://github.com/maximtop","line":477},{"title":"Michael Mok","target":"http://github.com/pmmmwh","line":477},{"title":"Seyyed Morteza Moosavi","target":"http://github.com/smmoosavi","line":477},{"title":"Tan75","target":"http://github.com/tan75","line":477},{"title":"Improved `nextDay` performance by roughly 50%.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2524","line":481},{"title":"Added more ordinal formatting to the Japanese locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2471","line":483},{"title":"Added a new `clamp` function that allows to bound a date to an interval.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2498","line":487},{"title":"Added Bosnian locale (bs).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2495","line":489},{"title":"Allowed passing `undefined` in the duration to add and sub functions.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2515","line":491},{"title":"Sasha Koss","target":"http://github.com/kossnocorp","line":495},{"title":"#2491","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/2491","line":499},{"title":"Lay","target":"http://github.com/brownsugar","line":503},{"title":"fturmel","target":"http://github.com/fturmel","line":503},{"title":"jwbth","target":"http://github.com/jwbth","line":503},{"title":"Sasha Koss","target":"http://github.com/kossnocorp","line":503},{"title":"Lucas Silva","target":"http://github.com/LucasHFS","line":503},{"title":"Anastasia Kobzar","target":"http://github.com/rikkalo","line":503},{"title":"Tan75","target":"http://github.com/tan75","line":503},{"title":"Fixed Taiwanese locale to use traditional Chinese and removed unnecessary spaces.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2436","line":507},{"title":"Fixed Russian locale to use correct long formats.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2478","line":509},{"title":"Added 18 new conversion functions","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2433","line":513},{"title":"Maxim Topciu","target":"http://github.com/maximtop","line":537},{"title":"Fixed IE11 support by babelifing the shorthand properties.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2467","line":541},{"title":"Aleksei Korzun","target":"http://github.com/a-korzun","line":545},{"title":"Mohammad ali Ali panah","target":"http://github.com/always-maap","line":545},{"title":"Jonas L","target":"http://github.com/jooola","line":545},{"title":"Maxim Topciu","target":"http://github.com/maximtop","line":545},{"title":"Tan75","target":"http://github.com/tan75","line":545},{"title":"`differenceInBusinessDays` now returns `NaN` instead of `Invalid Date` when an invalid argument is passed to the function.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2414","line":549},{"title":"Fixed `weekStartsOn` in Persian locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2430","line":551},{"title":"Sasha Koss","target":"http://github.com/kossnocorp","line":555},{"title":"Fixed a breaking change introduced by using modern default argument value syntax (see https://github.com/Hacker0x01/react-datepicker/issues/2870).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2423","line":559},{"title":"Aleksei Korzun","target":"http://github.com/a-korzun","line":563},{"title":"Christoph Stenglein","target":"http://github.com/cstenglein","line":563},{"title":"Clément Tamisier","target":"http://github.com/ctamisier","line":563},{"title":"Rubens Mariuzzo","target":"http://github.com/rmariuzzo","line":563},{"title":"Tan75","target":"http://github.com/tan75","line":563},{"title":"Made `formatDistanceStrict` return `12 months` instead of `1 year` when `unit: 'month'`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2411","line":567},{"title":"Added Haitian Creole (`ht`) locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2396","line":571},{"title":"Added Austrian German (`de-AT`) locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2362","line":572},{"title":"fturmel","target":"http://github.com/fturmel","line":576},{"title":"#2207","target":"https://github.com/