:265},{"title":"UTCDate","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/utc","line":275},{"title":"See more details","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/3208#issuecomment-1528592465","line":289},{"title":"Fixed Ukrainian (`uk`) locale grammar for `formatDistance`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3175","line":297},{"title":"Improved browser compatibility by transforming the code with `@babel/preset-env`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3167","line":299},{"title":"Fixed `sv` locale abbreviated months matcher.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3160","line":307},{"title":"Fixed `uk` locale abbreviated months matcher.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3139","line":309},{"title":"Fixed a breaking change in `intervalToDuration` by removing a recently introduced RangeError.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3153","line":311},{"title":"Fixed TypeScript and flow types for daysInYear constant.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3125","line":319},{"title":"Added `intlFormatDistance` function`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2173","line":327},{"title":"Added `setDefaultOptions` and `getDefaultOptions` functions that allow you to set default default locale, `weekStartsOn` and `firstWeekContainsDate`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3069","line":329},{"title":"Added `roundingMethod` option to `roundToNearestMinutes`.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3091","line":331},{"title":"Added Swiss Italian locale (`it-CH`).","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2886","line":333},{"title":"#2061","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/issues/2061","line":335},{"title":"Added Occitan (`oc`) locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/2106","line":335},{"title":"Added Belarusian Classic (`be-tarask`) locale.","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/3115","l