d shortenings in the Bulgarian locale","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1560","line":11},{"title":"Fixed regex for the May in the Portuguese locale","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1565","line":12},{"title":"Added `eachMonthOfInterval` and `eachYearOfInterval`","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/618","line":16},{"title":"Added `inclusive` option to `areIntervalsOverlapping","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/643","line":17},{"title":"Added `isExists` function that checks if the given date is exists","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/682","line":18},{"title":"Added `add` function to add seconds, minutes, hours, weeks, years in single call","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1581","line":19},{"title":"Added `sub` function, the opposite of `add`","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1583","line":20},{"title":"Added `Duration` type used in `add` and `sub`","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1583","line":21},{"title":"Added Azerbaijani (az) locale","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1547","line":22},{"title":"Added Moroccan Arabic (ar-MA) locale","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1578","line":23},{"title":"Reduced the total minified build size by 1Kb/4%","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1563","line":27},{"title":"Made all properties in `Locale` type optional","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1542","line":28},{"title":"Added missing properties to `Locale` type","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1542","line":29},{"title":"Add the locale code to `Locale` type","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1580","line":30},{"title":"Added support of space time separator to `parseJSON`","target":"https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/pull/1579","line":31},{"title":"Allowed up to 7 digits in milliseconds in `parseJSON`","target":"https://github.